guide: Play Pokémon Yellow and obtain all possible elements using only that game.
Play Pokémon Red until reaching Power Plant to catch Electabuzz.
Play Pokémon Blue until reaching Pokémon Mansion to catch Magmar.
Play Pokémon Red or Blue multiple times to trade starters.

In Pokémon Stadium, to get Surf Pikachu, use Mewtwo (Psychic, Ice Beam, Thunderbolt, Amnesia), Snorlax (Body Slam, Rest, Amnesia, Earthquake) and Pikachu (Thunder Wave, Flash, Thunderbolt, Quick Attack).

-Fastest way to level up is to transfer to Pokémon Crystal and use Lucky Egg and Exp Share. To train, Snorlax should use Shadow Ball (instead of Rest) and Pikachu should use Hidden Power/Return (instead of Flash).
-To beat other categories (ex: Gym Leader Castle) using rentals, check Speedrunning guides.
Check Generation I Version Compability Page
